gltools
------------------------------------------
GLTools library

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.0-0.221.g37920d33accd
  cygwin-devel-3.6.0-0.221.g37920d33accd
  libGL-devel-19.1.6-1
  libGL1-19.1.6-1
  libGLU-devel-9.0.2-1
  libgltools-devel-193-1bl2
  libgltools0-193-1bl2
  libglut-devel-3.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20240607-1
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  libGL-devel-19.1.6-1
  libGLU-devel-9.0.2-1
  libglut-devel-3.4.0-1
  libtool-2.5.3-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/msteinert/gltools

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/msteinert/gltools/archive/refs/tags/v193.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack gltools-193-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./gltools-193-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/gltools-193-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/gltools-193-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgltools0-193-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgltools-devel-193-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(gltools)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/gltools.README
  /usr/share/doc/gltools/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/gltools/README

(libgltools0)
  /usr/bin/cyggltools-0.dll

(libgltools-devel)
